::Striker/Prowl::

Striker shakes his head, continuing to run, "They can handle themselves. 
Right now we need to get moving from the Ark before the next attack."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl blinks as he hears Bluestreak say his name. He frowns. It felt so ... 
familiar.

"I'm Prowl... Although I don't know what you mean by 'that' Prowl."
